		"description": "<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-f298e4bd-7fff-f968-7a76-ea62d575fe59\">You can spend an artifact charge as a bonus action to attempt to offload the effects of your Accursed Affliction to another creature within 30 feet. The target makes a Charisma saving throw against your spell save DC. On a failed save, the target is affected as if by a </span><em>bestow lesser curse</em> spell, suffering the effect from that spell of your choosing and the effect of your curse is neutralized for as long as you maintain concentration on the <em>bestow lesser curse</em> effect, but you cannot use or benefit from Twisted Affliction, Greater Twisted Affliction, Mastered Affliction, or Critical Twisted Affliction until the effects of your curse return.</p>",
